<lyrics>[V1]
 1-(msẖ hạḥkylk msẖạkly wlạ hạsẖrḥ lk ẓrwfy
 mạ ạ̉nt ʿạrf ḥyạty wạ̉nt kạsẖf ạ̉mwry)2
 lkn ạ̉nạ jạylk ʿsẖạn ạ̉sẖwfk bạlʿyạn
 lmạ htḥḍr yạ gẖạly mjdk ymly̱ ạlmkạn
 ạlqrạr- (whsẖwfk .whsẖwfk wạ̉tmtʿ bạllqạ
 wbnwrk . wbnwrk tsẖrq ʿly̱ ạlmlạ)2
 2-(lmạ tsẖwfk ʿynyạ hạnsy̱ kl ạlly fyạ
 mạ ạ̉nt qlt fy klạmk ạ̉rmy ḥmwlk ʿlyạ )2
 wạ̉nạ lmạ hạjy wạ̉sẖwfk wạ̉tmtʿ mn ḥḍwrk
 thrb kl ạ̉ḥzạny wạ̉lms mjdk wạ̉sẖwfk
 3-(lmạ ạ̉sẖwfk yạ gẖạly ṣwrtk tmlạ kẖyạly
 tsẖfy ạlḍʿf ạlly fyạ ytbdl kl ḥạly)2
 tlms jrḥy bạ̹ydyk wtạkẖdny ʿly̱ mnkbyk
 wạ̉qwm mn ḍʿfy tạny wạ̉kẖd ạlqwh ạlly fyk</lyrics>
